### failure-test.http
### 用于验证 trade 模块失败场景、reconcile 模块异常状态流转与补偿逻辑

### =========================================================
### 0. 测试前准备：先查账户余额与流水
### =========================================================

### 查询用户1账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1

### 查询用户2账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2

### 查询用户1流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1/flows

### 查询用户2流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2/flows


### =========================================================
### 1. 重复 tradeNo 幂等测试
### 预期：
### - 第一次成功
### - 第二次被幂等拦截
### - trade_order 只有一条
### - 双方余额/流水只变化一次
### =========================================================

### 幂等测试-第一次
POST http://localhost:8083/trades/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tradeNo": "T_REPEAT_202604010001",
  "fromUserId": 1,
  "toUserId": 2,
  "amount": 50.00
}

### 幂等测试-第二次（相同 tradeNo）
POST http://localhost:8083/trades/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tradeNo": "T_REPEAT_202604010001",
  "fromUserId": 1,
  "toUserId": 2,
  "amount": 50.00
}

### 查询交易单
GET http://localhost:8083/trades/T_REPEAT_202604010001

### 查询用户1账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1

### 查询用户2账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2

### 查询用户1流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1/flows

### 查询用户2流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2/flows


### =========================================================
### 2. 余额不足测试
### 预期：
### - 返回余额不足
### - 交易单状态为失败或未成功
### - 双方余额不变
### - 无成功流水
### =========================================================

### 余额不足测试
POST http://localhost:8083/trades/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tradeNo": "T_FAIL_BALANCE_202604010001",
  "fromUserId": 1,
  "toUserId": 2,
  "amount": 99999.00
}

### 查询失败交易单
GET http://localhost:8083/trades/T_FAIL_BALANCE_202604010001

### 查询用户1账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1

### 查询用户2账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2

### 查询用户1流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1/flows

### 查询用户2流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2/flows


### =========================================================
### 3. 转出账户不存在
### 预期：
### - 返回账户不存在
### - 不应发生扣款/加款
### - 不应产生成功流水
### - 交易单状态为失败或未成功
### =========================================================

### 转出账户不存在
POST http://localhost:8083/trades/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tradeNo": "T_FAIL_FROM_NOT_EXIST_202604010001",
  "fromUserId": 999,
  "toUserId": 2,
  "amount": 50.00
}

### 查询交易单
GET http://localhost:8083/trades/T_FAIL_FROM_NOT_EXIST_202604010001

### 查询用户1账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1

### 查询用户2账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2

### 查询用户1流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1/flows

### 查询用户2流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/2/flows


### =========================================================
### 4. 转入账户不存在
### 预期：
### - 返回账户不存在
### - 交易单状态为失败
### - 若已发生扣款，应执行补偿退款
### - 转出账户最终余额恢复
### - 流水中可看到扣款与退款两条记录
### =========================================================

### 转入账户不存在
POST http://localhost:8083/trades/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tradeNo": "T_FAIL_TO_NOT_EXIST_202604010001",
  "fromUserId": 1,
  "toUserId": 999,
  "amount": 50.00
}

### 查询交易单
GET http://localhost:8083/trades/T_FAIL_TO_NOT_EXIST_202604010001

### 查询用户1账户
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1

### 查询用户1流水
GET http://localhost:8082/accounts/user/1/flows

### 查询对账分页
GET http://localhost:8084/reconcile/page?pageNum=1&pageSize=10


